Conduction of Energy Days in Lviv pursues triple goal: 
to inform city inhabitants about work done, trying to indicate potential threats to development of city energetic and climate in order to create safe energetic future for residents;
to familiarize them with main provisions of Sustainable energy action plan till year 2020;
propose to each of interested parties in the city to make contributions to development of  this document and its implementation.
Days are organized every year jointly by the Lviv city council and the Association "Energy Effective Cities of Ukraine" (EECU).
A great number of partners helps to organize different activities for various types of participants.

